headline: Selling Power Recognizes Paycom as a Top Sales Organization
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, July 14, 2025--Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE: PAYC) ("Paycom"), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, today announced its inclusion on Selling Power’s 2025 list of the 60 Best Companies to Sell For. The recognized companies demonstrated remarkable success and growth by elevating their sales teams to new heights.

headline: LRT Capital Management June 2025 Investor Update
summary: During the month of June the LRT Global Opportunities strategy returned -1.30% net of fees. Year-to-date, the strategy has returned +8.12%. Read more here.
